OL,3,CAttempted arson attack at Kenton
OL,4,CUnited Synagogue in Harrow overnight
OL,6,FPolice and fire crews responded to an
OL,7,Fattempted arson attack at Kenton
OL,8,FUnited Synagogue in north-west London
OL,9,Fovernight, the Community Security
OL,10,FTrust (CST) said.
OL,12,FIt caused minor smoke damage.
OL,14,FNo injuries or significant structural
OL,15,Fdamage was caused.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the charity, CST,
OL,18,Fsaid:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
