OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776687066
OL,3,CAttempted arson attack at Kenton
OL,4,CUnited Synagogue in Harrow overnight
OL,6,F"We are aware of another attempted
OL,7,Farson, this time targeting a synagogue
OL,8,Fin north London, following similar
OL,9,Frecent incidents targeting the Jewish
OL,10,Fcommunity in Finchley, Golders Green
OL,11,Fand Hendon.
OL,13,F"On this occasion there was minor
OL,14,Fsmoke damage to an internal room, but
OL,15,Fthere were no injuries and no
OL,16,Fsignificant structural damage.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
