PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776687066
OL,3,CAttempted arson attack at Kenton
OL,4,CUnited Synagogue in Harrow overnight
OL,6,F"We want to thank the Met Police and
OL,7,FLondon Fire Brigade for responding
OL,8,Fquickly and for all they are doing to
OL,9,Fprotect the Jewish community during
OL,10,Fthis unprecedented period.
OL,12,F"We are supporting the affected
OL,13,Flocation and are working closely with
OL,14,Fthe police as they investigate and
OL,15,Fseek to identify those responsible.
OL,17,F"We urge people to remain vigilant and
OL,18,Fto report any suspicious activity, at
OL,19,Fany time of day or night, to the
OL,20,Fpolice immediately on 999 and then to
OL,21,FCST."
